[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   between matter and the Temporal Topology scalar field. It is determined by fitting
[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   the predicted velocity anomaly from the scalar force model to the observed
[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   Doppler measurements from NASA's Deep Space Network.
[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008] 
