[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   Flybys are included in fitting only if the observed anomaly has signal-to-noise
[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   ratio ≥ 2. This prevents confirmation bias by excluding marginal detections.
[2026-05-10 15:10:42 UTC] [INFO    ] [STEP 008]   Current analysis: Will show count after fitting completes.
